      • getTargetPlatformBinary

        public static BuildTarget getTargetPlatformBinary​(Optional<BuildTarget> binary,
                                                  Optional<PatternMatchedCollection<BuildTarget>> platformBinary,
                                                  Flavor cxxPlatformFlavor)
        Returns a build target of the apple binary for the requested target platform.

        By default it's the binary that was provided using binary attribute, but in case platform_binary is specified and one of its patterns matches the target platform, it will be returned instead.
